Follow-up details: 

Operation implemented grouping of children with similarities together to avoid any type of child-on-child aggression and to avoid sexualized behaviors. During the physical follow up inspection children were observed to be in three different groups doing different activities. Sleeping arrangements have also been made for children that have sexualized behavior history. Staff were noted to be present outside of the children's bedrooms. Staffed interviewed also explained that they are to report any behaviors right away using an incident report form by the end of shift no exceptions. "
